320
01:10:53,266 --> 01:10:55,966
帆を上げろ お宝出航！
Raise the sails, treasures away!

321
01:10:56,266 --> 01:10:58,966
後悔したくない その思いが
The feeling of not wanting any regrets...

322
01:10:59,266 --> 01:11:02,466
追い風になる
...will become the wind at your back.

323
01:11:02,666 --> 01:11:05,466
あまたな思い出して
Recall the countless memories.

324
01:11:05,966 --> 01:11:09,966
私たちがいるから 最高にハッピーな運命を Yeah!
Since we're here, let's have the happiest destiny! Yeah!

325
01:11:13,666 --> 01:11:15,466
皆さん！次は早口ですが
Everyone! The next part is fast-paced!

326
01:11:15,666 --> 01:11:17,266
マリンちゃん噛まないでね！
Marine-chan, don't trip over your words!

327
01:11:17,466 --> 01:11:18,966
船長は噛みませんよ！
I won't trip over them!

328
